# Chat behavior interview (requestable)

Follow **`docs/maintainers/playbooks/workspace-kit-chat-behavior-interview.md`**.

- **Welcome:** **## The scribe’s quiz** + **begin** / **discard**; **`start` resets** — never mid-quiz.
